HEADWORD: Subvertebral
<hw>Sub*ver"te*bral</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Anat.)</fld>
<def>Situated beneath, or on the ventral side of, the vertebral column;
situated beneath, or inside of, the endoskeleton; hypaxial;
hyposkeletal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

